    <dict><key>cell</key><string>PSGroupCell</string><key>label</key><string>PHONEAURA 0.4.1</string><key>footerText</key><string>RootHide registration repair. PhoneAura Studio is installed on the Home Screen; this pane provides quick and emergency controls using the same PreferenceLoader structure as your working Next Solution tweaks.</string></dict>
